<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="es">

<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta http-equiv="X-UA-Compatible" content="IE=edge">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>
        <%= title %>
    </title>
    <link rel="shortcut icon" href="icon/patita.ico" type="image/x-icon">
    <link rel="stylesheet" href="https://unpkg.com/flowbite@1.5.3/dist/flowbite.min.css" />
</head>

<body>
    <%- include('partials/nav') %>

        <section class="bg-white dark:bg-gray-900">
            <div
                class="gap-8 items-center py-8 px-4 mx-auto max-w-screen-xl xl:gap-16 md:grid md:grid-cols-2 sm:py-16 lg:px-6">
                <img class="w-full dark:hidden" src="svg/logo.svg" alt="dashboard image">
                <div class="mt-4 md:mt-0">
                    <h2 class="mb-4 text-4xl tracking-tight font-extrabold text-gray-900 dark:text-white">About</h2>
                    <p class="mb-6 font-light text-gray-500 md:text-lg dark:text-gray-400">
                        We are the digital platform most focused on showing our animals throughout Peru, because we live
                        in a country with a lot of diversity, taking into account the coast, mountains and jungle,
                        therefore here you will see and have the opportunity to upload information about animals that
                        are not yet on the platform. We are pleased to be able to provide all the useful and quality
                        information to each of our readers, followers and users for the well-being of our Peruvian
                        culture.
                    </p>
                </div>
            </div>
        </section>
        <section class="bg-white dark:bg-gray-900">
            <div class="max-w-screen-xl px-4 py-8 mx-auto text-center lg:py-16 lg:px-6">
                <figure class="max-w-screen-md mx-auto">
                    <svg class="h-12 mx-auto mb-3 text-gray-400 dark:text-gray-600" viewBox="0 0 24 27" fill="none"
                        xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg">
                        <path
                            d="M14.017 18L14.017 10.609C14.017 4.905 17.748 1.039 23 0L23.995 2.151C21.563 3.068 20 5.789 20 8H24V18H14.017ZM0 18V10.609C0 4.905 3.748 1.038 9 0L9.996 2.151C7.563 3.068 6 5.789 6 8H9.983L9.983 18L0 18Z"
                            fill="currentColor" />
                    </svg>
                    <blockquote>
                        <p class="text-2xl font-medium text-gray-900 dark:text-white">
                            "Site Animals is just amazing. It contains a lake of information about our animals in the
                            Peruvian territory, it is also a very helpful platform for our students when looking for
                            information."
                        </p>
                    </blockquote>
                    <figcaption class="flex items-center justify-center mt-6 space-x-3">
                        <img class="w-6 h-6 rounded-full"
                            src="img/teacher.png"
                            alt="profile picture">
                        <div class="flex items-center divide-x-2 divide-gray-500 dark:divide-gray-700">
                            <div class="pr-3 font-medium text-gray-900 dark:text-white">Daniel Ramos</div>
                            <div class="pl-3 text-sm font-light text-gray-500 dark:text-gray-400">Docente de <span title="Juan Espinosa Medrano">JEM</span> </div>
                        </div>
                    </figcaption>
                </figure>
            </div>
        </section>
        <%- include('partials/footer') %>
</body>

</html>